Functions:
A function is reusable block of code
It can be call any where program
----Reusable code: using an existing code with out write the whole code again
Can use same code with different arguments to result

JS:
Key word = function
( )
Parameters = values(variables) which are declared inside the ( )
While defining
Arguments : values which are passed through the parameters
<script>
            function greet(){
                console.log("hello")
            }
            greet()
            console.log("hi bro")
            greet()
            console.log("hey")

        </script>
